        "faq_accordion": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "name": "t:names.accordion",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "caret",
            "dividers": true,
            "type_preset": "h5",
            "inherit_color_scheme": true,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "border": "none",
            "border_width": 1,
            "border_opacity": 100,
            "border_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {
            "faq_row_1": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Quels types d'appareils réparez-vous?",
                "open_by_default": true,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Nous réparons une grande variété d'appareils électroniques et électroménagers. </p><p>Liste des marques réparables sont : </p><ul><li>BE Power Equipment</li><li>Bissett</li><li>Bostitch</li><li>Dewalt</li><li>ET&F</li><li>Foresto</li><li>Makita</li><li>Max</li><li>Metabo-HPT</li><li>Milwaukee</li><li>Mi-T-M</li><li>Muro</li><li>Pneutools</li><li>QuikDrive</li><li>Senco</li><li>Spotnails</li><li>Stabila</li><li>Stiletto</li><li>Stinger</li><li>Simpson Strong-Tie</li></ul>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text"
              ]
            },
            "faq_row_2": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Combien de temps dure une réparation?",
                "open_by_default": true,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Le délai dépend du type de réparation et de la disponibilité des pièces. </p><ul><li><strong>Réception de l’outil brisé : </strong>48 à 72h </li><li><strong>Diagnostic</strong> : 1 à 3 semaines (variable selon le type d’outil)</li><li><strong>Réparation</strong> : 1 à 2 semaines (variable selon le type d’outil et la disponibilité des pièces)</li><li><strong>Délai de livraison</strong> : 48 à 7h</li></ul><p>Option réparation express : <strong>   </strong>      </p><ul><li><strong>Diagnostic </strong>: 24 à 48h</li><li><strong>Réparation</strong> : 2 à 14 jours selon la disponibilité des pièces.</li></ul>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text"
              ]
            },
            "faq_row_3": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Offrez-vous une garantie sur les réparations?",
                "open_by_default": true,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Politique de réparation (Frais, garantie, délais)</p><ul><li><strong>Frais de transport d’envoi</strong> : variables selon le lieu de départ (aux frais du client)</li><li><strong>Frais de soumission</strong> : 24,99$ (remboursés si le client accepte les frais de réparation)</li><li><strong>Taux horaire </strong>: 85,00$ (sauf si sous garantie)</li><li><strong>Pièces</strong> : variables selon les réparations (sauf si sous garantie)</li><li><strong>Garantie offerte</strong> : selon la garantie du manufacturier</li></ul>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "normal",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
